            "testName": "SAT Question Bank",
            "prompt": "The function $h$ is defined by $h\\left(x\\right)=4x+28$. The graph of $y=h\\left(x\\right)$ in the $xy$-plane has an $x$-intercept at $\\left(a,0\\right)$ and a $y$-intercept at $\\left(0,b\\right)$, where $a$ and $b$ are constants. What is the value of $a+b$?",
